1
00:00:50,780 --> 00:00:55,740
=Sugar and Lies=
(A Different Her: The Women's Trilogy)

2
00:00:56,820 --> 00:00:59,780
=Episode 24=
=Sugar and Lies=

3
00:01:03,960 --> 00:01:05,040
Boss.

4
00:01:05,040 --> 00:01:06,680
Maybe we can give it another shot.

5
00:01:07,040 --> 00:01:08,520
Besides, you just woke up.

6
00:01:08,520 --> 00:01:10,680
You've barely said a word
to Ding Daang yet.

7
00:01:10,680 --> 00:01:11,760
Otherwise, I feel like...

8
00:01:11,760 --> 00:01:12,600
Alright.

9
00:01:13,320 --> 00:01:14,560
Is everything set?

10
00:01:15,360 --> 00:01:16,480
Are you sure about this?

11
00:01:17,400 --> 00:01:18,990
After all, you poured your heart into it.

12
00:01:19,720 --> 00:01:22,080
Aren't you going to regret
shutting it down?

13
00:01:25,440 --> 00:01:26,800
It's fine.

14
00:01:26,800 --> 00:01:27,840
Trust me.

15
00:01:29,560 --> 00:01:30,400
What about you?

16
00:01:36,320 --> 00:01:39,400
I just need a moment alone.

17
00:01:39,400 --> 00:01:40,240
Don't worry.

18
00:01:42,640 --> 00:01:44,440
At least say goodbye to Ding Daang, okay?

19
00:01:46,360 --> 00:01:47,200
I will.

20
00:01:49,480 --> 00:01:50,920
It's just that... this thing...

21
00:01:50,920 --> 00:01:52,360
Don't let her find out, okay?

22
00:01:54,080 --> 00:01:55,560
She's already done enough for me.

23
00:01:56,040 --> 00:01:56,880
As for the rest,

24
00:01:57,440 --> 00:01:58,640
I can handle it on my own.

25
00:01:59,400 --> 00:02:00,240
(Ding Daang,)

26
00:02:01,080 --> 00:02:01,960
(please forgive me.)

27
00:02:02,960 --> 00:02:04,560
(Forgive me for leaving for a while.)

28
00:02:06,040 --> 00:02:08,080
(Wait for a perfect Chen Aming.)

29
00:02:08,320 --> 00:02:09,880
(I'll come back for you.)

30
00:02:16,040 --> 00:02:16,920
Ding Daang.

31
00:02:16,920 --> 00:02:18,040
What are you doing here?

32
00:02:19,120 --> 00:02:20,840
Didn't I tell you
to wait for me at home?

33
00:02:21,520 --> 00:02:22,880
I was craving chestnut cake.

34
00:02:23,200 --> 00:02:24,880
You could've just texted me, you know.

35
00:02:26,120 --> 00:02:26,960
I wanted to see you.

36
00:02:35,080 --> 00:02:35,920
Ding Daang.

37
00:02:54,040 --> 00:02:55,440
I might have to leave for a while.

38
00:02:59,440 --> 00:03:00,400
What happened?

39
00:03:03,600 --> 00:03:04,680
Getting scared again?

40
00:03:07,880 --> 00:03:09,240
How could I not be?

41
00:03:10,440 --> 00:03:11,800
I almost killed you.

42
00:03:14,840 --> 00:03:15,880
It's okay.

43
00:03:16,400 --> 00:03:17,240
See?

44
00:03:17,840 --> 00:03:20,000
I'm right here, safe and sound.

45
00:03:32,750 --> 00:03:35,870
笙ｪI'm no longer tangled up inside笙ｪ

46
00:03:39,360 --> 00:03:40,200
Ding Daang.

47
00:03:41,080 --> 00:03:41,920
Don't say anything.

48
00:03:43,360 --> 00:03:44,200
Go ahead.

49
00:03:45,200 --> 00:03:46,040
I'll wait for you.

50
00:03:48,600 --> 00:03:49,840
Please give me some time.

51
00:03:54,640 --> 00:03:58,280
笙ｪWe keep each other company笙ｪ

52
00:03:58,280 --> 00:04:03,270
笙ｪIf this is as far as we can go笙ｪ

53
00:04:04,180 --> 00:04:08,850
笙ｪIt must be because of fate笙ｪ

54
00:04:08,850 --> 00:04:13,050
笙ｪIt's not something I can keep
just because I want to笙ｪ

55
00:04:13,050 --> 00:04:13,960
(Keep Love)
Boss.

56
00:04:13,960 --> 00:04:16,080
You still have time to regret this.

57
00:04:17,200 --> 00:04:18,040
Xibei.

58
00:04:18,680 --> 00:04:19,960
Do you remember

59
00:04:19,960 --> 00:04:21,480
the first time you saw me?

60
00:04:26,040 --> 00:04:28,120
You said my algorithm
was complete trash.

61
00:04:28,920 --> 00:04:30,360
That's because you overturned

62
00:04:30,360 --> 00:04:32,560
the entire model I carefully designed.

63
00:04:32,560 --> 00:04:34,360
Turns out your algorithm was right.

64
00:04:37,960 --> 00:04:38,800
Alright.

65
00:04:39,520 --> 00:04:40,360
Come on.

66
00:04:41,920 --> 00:04:43,360
It's not a final goodbye.

67
00:04:43,960 --> 00:04:45,120
If Keep Love's gone, so be it.

68
00:04:45,800 --> 00:04:46,720
But you, man.

69
00:04:46,880 --> 00:04:48,360
You better come back in one piece.

70
00:04:52,200 --> 00:04:54,240
Who's the one acting like
it's a final goodbye now?

71
00:04:57,320 --> 00:04:58,160
Happy love life.

72
00:04:59,720 --> 00:05:00,660
Yeah, happy love life.

73
00:05:01,200 --> 00:05:02,280
What if he picks on me

74
00:05:02,280 --> 00:05:03,560
after you left?

75
00:05:03,840 --> 00:05:04,720
Don't worry.

76
00:05:05,120 --> 00:05:05,960
When he's away,

77
00:05:06,080 --> 00:05:06,920
you've still got me.

78
00:05:10,560 --> 00:05:11,400
My friend.

79
00:05:12,960 --> 00:05:14,520
Nothing else really matters.

80
00:05:15,600 --> 00:05:16,440
You coming back

81
00:05:16,860 --> 00:05:17,800
is what really matters.

82
00:05:23,880 --> 00:05:25,320
Your boss will always have your back.

83
00:05:37,040 --> 00:05:37,880
I'm leaving.

84
00:06:04,940 --> 00:06:11,660
(Keep Love)

85
00:06:17,900 --> 00:06:24,220
(Suga Love)

86
00:06:38,760 --> 00:06:39,920
Ding Daang.

87
00:06:42,240 --> 00:06:43,080
Have a seat.

88
00:06:51,200 --> 00:06:53,400
I never thought you'd let him go.

89
00:06:53,920 --> 00:06:55,400
I figured you'd stop him.

90
00:06:56,520 --> 00:06:57,600
Or maybe...

91
00:06:57,600 --> 00:06:59,000
keep him from wrecking Keep Love.

92
00:06:59,920 --> 00:07:00,960
Do you think

93
00:07:01,320 --> 00:07:02,640
I'd hold on to him no matter what

94
00:07:02,640 --> 00:07:03,520
like before?

95
00:07:03,920 --> 00:07:04,760
No,

96
00:07:04,800 --> 00:07:06,000
I just feel like

97
00:07:06,000 --> 00:07:07,640
you gave him so much

98
00:07:07,640 --> 00:07:09,440
and even hurt yourself for him.

99
00:07:10,280 --> 00:07:11,520
But in the end...

100
00:07:14,800 --> 00:07:16,040
If what he needs is time,

101
00:07:17,440 --> 00:07:18,420
let's give him some time.

102
00:07:20,120 --> 00:07:21,520
If he needs to stop Keep Love

103
00:07:21,520 --> 00:07:22,640
just to find himself again,

104
00:07:23,320 --> 00:07:24,320
then I'll stand by him.

105
00:07:25,360 --> 00:07:26,240
But,

106
00:07:26,240 --> 00:07:27,440
what if he never comes back?

107
00:07:30,840 --> 00:07:31,680
Xibei,

108
00:07:32,520 --> 00:07:33,440
love means trust.

109
00:07:36,400 --> 00:07:37,240
Ding Daang,

110
00:07:38,080 --> 00:07:38,960
I got it.

111
00:07:39,280 --> 00:07:40,120
Thank you.

112
00:07:42,360 --> 00:07:43,200
The cake's here.

113
00:07:45,760 --> 00:07:46,600
Here you go.

114
00:07:46,760 --> 00:07:47,600
Have a taste.

115
00:07:48,520 --> 00:07:49,680
See if today's cake

116
00:07:49,680 --> 00:07:50,880
is sweeter than usual.

117
00:08:00,400 --> 00:08:01,240
It really is.

118
00:08:02,400 --> 00:08:03,990
Feels like there's something extra in it.

119
00:08:08,940 --> 00:08:11,140
(Utopia)

120
00:08:12,480 --> 00:08:13,320
Don't worry.

121
00:08:13,640 --> 00:08:15,040
Your brother will come back.

122
00:08:15,280 --> 00:08:16,120
You really think so?

123
00:08:16,640 --> 00:08:18,080
What if he comes back but changes?

124
00:08:21,920 --> 00:08:23,000
No matter who he becomes,

125
00:08:23,000 --> 00:08:24,040
he'll always be my boss.

126
00:08:25,760 --> 00:08:27,240
You know, I honestly feel like

127
00:08:27,240 --> 00:08:29,160
Ding Daang is incredibly brave.

128
00:08:29,560 --> 00:08:30,640
If it were me,

129
00:08:30,640 --> 00:08:32,880
I'd never wait for someone
who's changed.

130
00:08:33,800 --> 00:08:34,640
Hold on.

131
00:08:37,120 --> 00:08:38,600
What's that supposed to mean?

132
00:08:39,720 --> 00:08:41,720
Are you saying I'm not worth...?

133
00:08:42,080 --> 00:08:42,920
You?

134
00:08:43,160 --> 00:08:45,200
I'd recognize you
even if you turned to ashes.

135
00:08:48,200 --> 00:08:49,040
Come on,

136
00:08:50,880 --> 00:08:51,720
cheers.

137
00:08:58,530 --> 00:08:59,400
The live started.

138
00:08:59,400 --> 00:09:00,240
Look.

139
00:09:01,000 --> 00:09:02,600
Dear Keep Love users,

140
00:09:02,600 --> 00:09:03,440
good evening.

141
00:09:03,760 --> 00:09:06,160
Today's livestream is a bit different.

142
00:09:06,760 --> 00:09:07,600
Yes, it is.

143
00:09:08,040 --> 00:09:09,680
It's not about a product update,

144
00:09:09,680 --> 00:09:10,960
nor a relationship Q&A.

145
00:09:11,480 --> 00:09:12,800
We're here

146
00:09:13,440 --> 00:09:14,560
to say a proper goodbye.

147
00:09:15,200 --> 00:09:16,720
When we created Keep Love,

148
00:09:16,720 --> 00:09:18,080
our goal was to help everyone

149
00:09:18,080 --> 00:09:19,320
find their perfect love.

150
00:09:20,240 --> 00:09:21,440
We once believed

151
00:09:21,440 --> 00:09:22,920
that love could be measured by data.

152
00:09:23,440 --> 00:09:24,280
But

153
00:09:24,400 --> 00:09:25,240
we were wrong.

154
00:09:25,590 --> 00:09:26,440
Love

155
00:09:26,440 --> 00:09:27,840
lives in those moments

156
00:09:28,080 --> 00:09:29,800
that can never be measured.

157
00:09:30,160 --> 00:09:31,040
So starting today,

158
00:09:31,360 --> 00:09:33,160
we've decided to
officially close Keep Love,

159
00:09:33,680 --> 00:09:34,800
not because we failed,

160
00:09:35,240 --> 00:09:36,360
but because...

161
00:09:36,360 --> 00:09:37,240
we've realized

162
00:09:37,880 --> 00:09:38,720
there are some paths

163
00:09:39,200 --> 00:09:40,520
we have to walk on our own.

164
00:09:41,160 --> 00:09:42,240
And some answers

165
00:09:42,240 --> 00:09:44,560
can only be found
through genuine connection.

166
00:09:45,500 --> 00:09:47,140
Thank you for being part of this journey.

167
00:09:47,400 --> 00:09:49,120
All your data in Keep Love

168
00:09:49,120 --> 00:09:50,440
will be securely preserved.

169
00:09:51,120 --> 00:09:52,000
Starting today,

170
00:09:52,360 --> 00:09:54,400
let's forget the matching data from it.

171
00:09:55,320 --> 00:09:56,960
Look into each other's eyes

172
00:09:57,800 --> 00:10:00,160
and feel the warmth that's real.

173
00:10:00,840 --> 00:10:02,360
Express yourselves, even if awkwardly,

174
00:10:02,360 --> 00:10:03,400
and embrace with courage.

175
00:10:07,320 --> 00:10:08,160
Love

176
00:10:08,540 --> 00:10:09,620
doesn't need an algorithm.

177
00:10:10,840 --> 00:10:12,040
But a sincere heart.

178
00:10:33,400 --> 00:10:35,980
笙ｪThat song suddenly started playing笙ｪ

179
00:10:36,540 --> 00:10:38,730
笙ｪAnd I thought of you again笙ｪ

180
00:10:39,530 --> 00:10:44,440
笙ｪEven though I swore to the world
we were done笙ｪ

181
00:10:45,500 --> 00:10:48,060
笙ｪAll my friends laughed at me笙ｪ

182
00:10:48,460 --> 00:10:51,240
笙ｪWhy can't I just let it go笙ｪ

183
00:10:51,240 --> 00:10:52,740
(Suga Love)

184
00:10:52,740 --> 00:10:56,760
笙ｪBut how could they ever know
how good you were to me笙ｪ

185
00:10:57,150 --> 00:11:00,160
笙ｪI'm falling into
the swamp of your charm笙ｪ

186
00:11:00,410 --> 00:11:03,060
笙ｪIt's painful yet feels so right笙ｪ

187
00:11:03,220 --> 00:11:05,790
笙ｪAs the endless night unfolds笙ｪ

188
00:11:05,790 --> 00:11:08,520
笙ｪI toss and turn, can't fall asleep笙ｪ

189
00:11:10,250 --> 00:11:13,440
笙ｪYou keep running through my mind笙ｪ

190
00:11:13,440 --> 00:11:16,500
笙ｪNothing matters more than you笙ｪ

191
00:11:16,750 --> 00:11:17,880
笙ｪWhy?笙ｪ

192
00:11:18,270 --> 00:11:22,030
笙ｪYou walked out of my world笙ｪ

193
00:11:22,340 --> 00:11:25,170
笙ｪYou're my only cure笙ｪ

194
00:11:25,330 --> 00:11:28,590
(Suga Love)
笙ｪCan you give me one more hug?笙ｪ

195
00:11:30,340 --> 00:11:34,640
笙ｪDid you hear me say please don't go笙ｪ

196
00:11:36,470 --> 00:11:38,870
笙ｪThat song keeps playing on repeat笙ｪ

197
00:11:39,430 --> 00:11:41,780
笙ｪFeels like
everything has frozen in time笙ｪ

198
00:11:42,430 --> 00:11:47,630
笙ｪI wonder what you're doing now笙ｪ

199
00:11:48,180 --> 00:11:51,060
笙ｪAre you really happier than before?笙ｪ

200
00:11:51,260 --> 00:11:54,050
笙ｪLiving the life you always wanted笙ｪ

201
00:11:55,710 --> 00:11:59,620
笙ｪThe final note faded away笙ｪ

202
00:12:00,210 --> 00:12:02,530
笙ｪAs the final note gently falls笙ｪ

203
00:12:02,530 --> 00:12:05,330
笙ｪLet it be.
Maybe I was just holding on too tight笙ｪ

204
00:12:05,330 --> 00:12:07,580
笙ｪRoses are meant to bloom someday笙ｪ

205
00:12:07,770 --> 00:12:12,650
笙ｪLook up, you'll see a sky full of stars笙ｪ

206
00:12:13,180 --> 00:12:16,300
笙ｪYou keep running through my mind笙ｪ

207
00:12:16,300 --> 00:12:19,340
笙ｪNothing matters more than you笙ｪ

208
00:12:19,620 --> 00:12:20,780
笙ｪWhy?笙ｪ

209
00:12:21,180 --> 00:12:25,020
笙ｪYou walked out of my world笙ｪ

210
00:12:25,260 --> 00:12:28,220
笙ｪYou're my only cure笙ｪ

211
00:12:28,220 --> 00:12:31,340
笙ｪCan you give me one more hug?笙ｪ

212
00:12:33,220 --> 00:12:37,220
笙ｪDid you hear me say please don't go笙ｪ

213
00:12:37,220 --> 00:12:40,180
笙ｪMy world once shined because of you笙ｪ

214
00:12:40,180 --> 00:12:43,020
笙ｪI even forgot how small I was笙ｪ

215
00:12:43,220 --> 00:12:46,020
笙ｪAs long as
there's still fire in my heart笙ｪ

216
00:12:46,300 --> 00:12:49,100
笙ｪI won't let tears blur my eyes笙ｪ

217
00:12:49,300 --> 00:12:51,980
笙ｪSilently I pray for you笙ｪ

218
00:12:52,260 --> 00:12:55,300
笙ｪWishing you a better life than mine笙ｪ

219
00:12:56,980 --> 00:13:02,340
笙ｪIt no longer matters
if you're not by my side笙ｪ

220
00:13:16,180 --> 00:13:16,720
(No animals were harmed during filming.)

221
00:13:16,720 --> 00:13:17,270
(All animal scenes were conducted
under professional supervision)

222
00:13:17,270 --> 00:13:17,840
(in a safe, controlled environment.)

223
00:13:17,840 --> 00:13:18,390
(The portrayal of dissociative
