(please seek professional help)

227
00:13:20,300 --> 00:13:21,140
(and follow medical advice.)

228
00:13:40,840 --> 00:13:47,840
笙ｪI forgot this is a movie meant for one笙ｪ

229
00:13:52,240 --> 00:13:59,600
笙ｪSomehow you're still here,
crying with me笙ｪ

230
00:14:04,040 --> 00:14:06,000
笙ｪThey say笙ｪ

231
00:14:06,400 --> 00:14:14,800
笙ｪLovers should never hold hands
while watching a sad movie笙ｪ

232
00:14:15,320 --> 00:14:18,280
笙ｪSome endings cannot be changed笙ｪ

233
00:14:18,520 --> 00:14:24,440
笙ｪThey don't belong in sweet memories笙ｪ

234
00:14:25,840 --> 00:14:31,600
笙ｪI've already lost you笙ｪ

235
00:14:31,600 --> 00:14:37,080
笙ｪThinking of it takes my breath away笙ｪ

236
00:14:37,360 --> 00:14:43,320
笙ｪThe movie ends, so many couples around笙ｪ

237
00:14:43,320 --> 00:14:48,120
笙ｪYet none were ever like us笙ｪ

238
00:14:49,200 --> 00:14:53,240
笙ｪThe past will always pass笙ｪ

239
00:14:53,560 --> 00:15:01,160
笙ｪIf you could still hold me tight
in your arms笙ｪ

240
00:15:01,640 --> 00:15:04,880
笙ｪI'd believe
that there are miracles in love笙ｪ

241
00:15:05,440 --> 00:15:11,080
笙ｪI'd prove
that I'm still in love with you笙ｪ

242
00:15:13,560 --> 00:15:17,080
笙ｪI've learned how to cherish
what we had笙ｪ

243
00:15:17,080 --> 00:15:23,320
笙ｪBut sadly, it's not you笙ｪ
